🟢 Backend
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- written in pure PHP without frameworks. 🔒
- however it can be overridden with a framework module.

- If your backend or framework uses a database, 
  you must follow the constraints of the Database module.

- mandatory to enable an HTTPS connection for all aspects

- FORMS and user INPUT validation is handled on backend ⛔
  
❓ what is framework


🟢 Web modules
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Use a framework to build the backend 		(Major)

- Use a database for the backend. 		(Minor)

🟢 Devops modules
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

- Designing the backend as microservices.	(Major)
